Linda Marsh https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linda_Marsh 0 Linda Marsh (born Linda Cracovaner, February 8, 1939) is an American actress of film, stage, and television. She was nominated for a Golden Globe Award for her performance in Elia Kazan's 1963 film America, America.
